title: Koi Nante, Honki de Yatte Dousuruno?
overview: 27-year-old romance-free girl VS. Seta romance boy. Stability-oriented early marriage less wife VS. In translation mysterious chef. Beloved and addicted Papa Katsu Girls VS. Mysterious Yin-Yang Boys. A group image love story woven by 6 men and women who "can't get serious about love"!
